<div class='profile-header__intro'>
<div class='profile-header__intro__inner'>
<h1 class='h2 profile-header__name'>Hyeonseo Lee</h1>
<div class='p2 profile-header__summary'>
Activist
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class='hide-sm'>
<ul class='sl profile-header__flairs__inner'>
<li class='profile-header__flair'>
<a class="profile-header__flair__link" href="http://www.ted.com/participate/discuss/badges">TED Speaker</a>
</li>
<li class='profile-header__flair'>
<a class="profile-header__flair__link" href="http://www.ted.com/participate/discuss/badges">TED Attendee</a>
</li>
</ul>

</div>
<div class='profile-header__links'>
<div class='profile-header__links__inner'>
